des: Sunny Radio New Jersey offers a custom blend of Soft & Easy Favorites from the 60's through today! No other station comes close to what we deliver song after song, hour after hour! If you yearn for the forgotten favorites from the Carpenters, Barbra Streisand, Johnny Mathis, Kenny Rogers and Barry Manilow to the modern day classics from John Mayer, Luther Vandross, Mariah Carey, Michael Bolton, Michael Bublè and more, then you've found your new home great music around the clock! You will also find all the Full Service elements needed to get you through your day like ABC News, Local News from the "Central Jersey Newsroom" along with Traffic and Weather. Welcome to the ALL NEW Sunny Radio New Jersey and Thanks for Listening!
